vote.text: Pursuant to the provisions of H. Res. 772, H. Con. Res. 191 is considered passed House.

bill.summary:
(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)
Directs the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make technical corrections in the enrollment of H.R. 2918 (FY2010 legislative branch appropriations and continuing resolution).
